data.description:
Location, Location!! This Gorgeous open-floor plan Home is elegant and clean. 

Enter into the greater room with luxury vinyl wood look flooring, newer shoe molding, and recessed lighting. The main level foyer has custom-built wood lockers, an open family room featuring a stone fireplace flanked by built-in cabinets, and a shiplap wall. The other end of the family room has built-in cabinets with a mini-fridge and floating shelves, perfect for family and friends entertaining, and a Full bath off of the family room.

The kitchen is a dream with white & gray cabinets and crown molding, featuring a center island with seating for four and an eat-in kitchen space for a gathering area. Upstairs boasts an updated full bathroom that connects to the magnificent master and two more bedrooms, All bedrooms have new carpet flooring.

The basement is spacious and has built-in shelves for storage. 

Newer washer and dryer stay, plus brand new fridge and stove. Vinyl siding, gutters, and downspouts 2018. The two-in-one boiler system by Navien delivers instant and constant hot water and heats the home. The Roof was installed in 2011 and Central Air was installed on 11/2021.

This Development is close to shopping malls, hospitals, pharmacies, and convenience stores, Applewood Swim and Tennis Club. Sidewalks throughout development.
